attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KJYLEVZ7zfmge1xZlCL_display_text
attribs.current: If the horse moves at least 20 ft. straight toward a creature and then hits it with a hooves attack on the same turn, that target must succeed on a DC 14 Strength saving throw or be knocked prone. If the target is prone, the horse can make another attack with its hooves against it as a bonus action.

attribs.name: repeating_trait_-KJYLYHy1bqnAvZ6nEsU_display_text
attribs.current: Whenever the Elk hits an enemy with a ram attack, it can use its bonus action to make another ram attack against a target adjacent to the original.
